text: Plishkino () is a rural locality (a village) in Dubrovskoye Rural Settlement, Yelovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 118 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km WSW from Yelovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yelovsky District
title: Plishkino
